# Section 1
## What's AWS?
Its a Cloud Provider of several services that you can use on **demand** and **scale** easly
* Netflix is powered by AWS
![Alt text](images/awsservices.png)
* With aws we can build sophisticated, scalable applications 
* Use cases include
    * Enterprise IT
    * Backup & Storage
    * Big Data analytics
    * Website hosting
    * Mobile & Social Apps
    * Gaming
